{"tid":1727363,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"二噁英毒氣會係民意戰既下一個關鍵，可以拉攏藍絲","createTime":"2019-11-16T12:00:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T12:18:27.000Z","uid":54303,"like":84,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"c5e970cd9f1056bb94917d886d1f6ba5752c536f","tid":1727363,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T12:00:47.000Z","msg":"二噁英係全香港人切身關注既問題，連藍絲都會關心自己會唔會生cancer。所以請各位多加關注，多做宣傳。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外：<br />\n有專業知識既，可以調查下戰區既污染程度，尤其旺角、屯門、中大；<br />\n係記者既，唔該日日問班狗官/曱甴二噁英想點處理，<br />\n最理想係逼班曱甴唔再放TG；<br />\n選區議會既，唔該將毒氣變做區選議題，泛民朋友唔該承諾當選後會跟進自己果區既二噁英問題；<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">最後，示威遊行唔該加多句：「二噁英、毒死人」！</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n二噁英要成為下一個主要議題，唔該大家日日提、天天講、大大力屌班曱甴毒死人！我要全香港人都知自己有機會中毒！"},{"pid":"42a3c528bb0112e96ea93e142c2c8ed9f66a57d1","tid":1727363,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T12:00:58.000Z","msg":"認同就幫我推爆佢"},{"pid":"6c710c99dc456599c139063ae3c59c806ec7fbc5","tid":1727363,"uid":233156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T12:01:19.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f05eb7f313a831b3ca3e711f7013288157783c6a","tid":1727363,"uid":34953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T12:03:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"888981d4e6318dccd0683d061dcfd272ead0a744","tid":1727363,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T12:03:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ab3d39ae13ec96ca09ce46d5af5f5ed5383cf855","tid":1727363,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T12:04:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aac0f27aec746142291f0c6f31bddc7499e49601","tid":1727363,"uid":304663,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T12:04:44.000Z","msg":"係。但藍絲會話，你地唔（搞事），警又點會放tg。點破呢句？"},{"pid":"2cf5c422891f73fc67af576955abdd924f83944f","tid":1727363,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11